All Classes

Class Description
AbstractGraph
Abstract base class for graphs.
BreadthFirstSearch
Class to implement the breadth-first search algorithm.
DepthFirstSearch
Class to implement the DepthFirstSearch search algorithm.
Edge
An Edge represents a relationship between two vertices.
Graph
Interface to specify a Graph ADT.
LinkedListGraph
A LinkedListGraph is an extension of the AbstractGraph abstract class that uses an 2D LinkedList to represent the edges.
ListGraph
A ListGraph is an extension of the AbstractGraph abstract class that uses an array of lists to represent the edges.
MatrixGraph
A MatrixGraph is an implementation of the Graph abstract class that uses an array to represent the edges.
